hree gold medals and a bronze.\", \"from\": 2180, \"to\": 2315, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2221, \"end\": 2241, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kerri_Walsh_Jennings\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kerri Walsh Jennings\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q15117302\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kerri_Walsh_Jennings\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kerri_Walsh_Jennings\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the momentum\", \"from\": 2201, \"to\": 2213}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S. beach volleyball player\", \"from\": 2243, \"to\": 2275}, {\"ngram\": \"three gold medals\", \"from\": 2284, \"to\": 2301}, {\"ngram\": \"a bronze\", \"from\": 2306, \"to\": 2314}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And we need to broaden it, because it can not be once in a while.\", \"from\": 2316, \"to\": 2382, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It can not be once every four years, at a special event like this.\", \"from\": 2383, \"to\": 2449, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a special event\", \"from\": 2423, \"to\": 2438}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We need it 365, 24-7, because women are 50% of the population.\\\"\", \"from\": 2450, \"to\": 2513, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 2480, \"to\": 2485}, {\"ngram\": \"50%\", \"from\": 2490, \"to\": 2493}, {\"ngram\": \"the population\", \"from\": 2497, \"to\": 2511}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The runway show, called PARITY Paris, was hosted by the 4TheWalk clothing and merchandise brand at a restaurant next to Paris' famed Palais Garnier opera house, in partnership with Coca-Cola.\", \"from\": 2515, \"to\": 2706, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2546, \"end\": 2551, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.242099739612728e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2635, \"